
<p>You will recall that in September 2022, Figma entered into <a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2022/09/15/adobe-figma">an agreement for a $20 billion acquisition by Adobe</a>, but <a href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/12/18/figma-adobe-ixnay-on-the-acquisitionyay">abandoned the deal 15 months later</a>.</p>

